WEBVTT

00:54.000 --> 00:55.060
Hurry up. Let's go.

00:57.840 --> 00:58.400
Hurry up.

00:58.560 --> 00:59.160
Okay.

01:00.400 --> 01:01.060
I'm coming.

01:01.760 --> 01:03.760
You know what? We might actually have to chop wood.

01:03.760 --> 01:04.560
I told you so.

01:11.840 --> 01:12.640
Here it is.

01:25.120 --> 01:26.200
If you're tired,

01:26.880 --> 01:28.440
you can leave anytime.

01:30.080 --> 01:31.840
It's a new society now.

01:32.160 --> 01:34.620
Masters and apprentices can choose freely.

01:35.520 --> 01:36.600
In the past,

01:37.440 --> 01:39.800
would you dare speak to your master like that?

01:39.800 --> 01:40.400
Master.

01:40.680 --> 01:42.800
There are so many people out there offering me money to fire kilns,

01:42.800 --> 01:43.660
but I didn't go.

01:45.360 --> 01:47.160
With your skills,

01:47.200 --> 01:49.530
you dare go out and make a fool of yourself?

01:49.880 --> 01:51.479
Where am I lacking?

01:51.520 --> 01:52.479
Why won't you let me

01:52.479 --> 01:53.539
work at Weijiayao?

01:54.640 --> 01:55.280
Mr. Wei.

01:57.720 --> 01:58.360
Mr. Wei.

01:59.280 --> 01:59.810
Guan Lin,

02:00.640 --> 02:01.320
you're here.

02:01.320 --> 02:01.780
Mr. Wei.

02:03.000 --> 02:04.440
Our class this afternoon

02:05.120 --> 02:06.850
will be held here at Weijiayao.

02:07.320 --> 02:08.050
Is that okay?

02:08.400 --> 02:10.560
You led the restoration of this kiln.

02:10.600 --> 02:11.720
If you want to see it,

02:11.720 --> 02:12.960
how could I stop you?

02:15.000 --> 02:16.000
Guan Lin.

02:16.320 --> 02:17.250
Take them there.

02:18.040 --> 02:19.480
Mr. Yue, this way.

02:19.840 --> 02:20.440
Come.

02:21.440 --> 02:22.440
You stubborn old man.

02:22.440 --> 02:24.440
Stop being so harsh with your words.

02:25.920 --> 02:27.400
What's Mr. Wei's background?

02:27.400 --> 02:29.600
He doesn't even show respect to Mr. Yue.

02:30.040 --> 02:31.120
In Jingdezhen's traditional porcelain making,

02:31.120 --> 02:32.650
there are 72 steps in total.

02:32.680 --> 02:35.000
The most important one is firing the kiln.

02:35.000 --> 02:36.320
There's a saying in the industry:

02:36.320 --> 02:38.200
"Success or failure depends on the kiln fire."

02:38.200 --> 02:39.160
Mr. Wei is the industry's

02:39.160 --> 02:40.760
renowned chief kiln master.

02:40.800 --> 02:42.280
He is responsible for watching the fire.

02:42.280 --> 02:43.040
Mr. Yue.

02:43.200 --> 02:44.930
We looked at the photos before,

02:45.280 --> 02:47.560
and the roof of the kiln had partially collapsed.

02:47.560 --> 02:48.960
How exactly did you repair it

02:48.960 --> 02:50.240
so that it can reach the level

02:50.240 --> 02:51.770
of normal use like it is now?

02:51.800 --> 02:53.880
The repair work by Mr. Yue's expert team

02:53.880 --> 02:57.640
is called kiln construction and repair in our professional jargon.

02:57.640 --> 02:59.440
To ensure that the repaired kiln

02:59.480 --> 03:01.040
can operate normally,

03:01.080 --> 03:03.400
Mr. Yue first used the blueprints of Weijiayao

03:03.400 --> 03:04.640
passed down from his master

03:04.640 --> 03:07.920
to precisely calculate the proportions

03:07.920 --> 03:09.560
and dimensions of the entire structure.

03:09.560 --> 03:10.920
Then he led the workers

03:10.920 --> 03:13.050
in piecing it together purely by hand.

03:13.400 --> 03:14.040
Actually,

03:14.280 --> 03:16.480
in restoring a perfect arched kiln roof,

03:16.480 --> 03:17.740
every step is crucial.

03:18.120 --> 03:19.120
Not only must each layer of kiln bricks

03:19.120 --> 03:20.780
be evenly staggered inwards,

03:20.960 --> 03:21.600
but

03:21.960 --> 03:22.800
the bricks and mortar

03:22.800 --> 03:24.600
must also be optimally matched.

03:25.040 --> 03:26.640
On the one hand, it's for firm adhesion

03:26.640 --> 03:27.720
to minimize gaps.

03:28.240 --> 03:29.240
On the other hand,

03:30.000 --> 03:32.060
you must also use the tension created

03:32.360 --> 03:34.079
by the elliptical arrangement of the kiln bricks

03:34.079 --> 03:35.079
to ensure the roof

03:35.360 --> 03:37.840
doesn't collapse while converging inwards.

03:37.840 --> 03:38.880
Wow, Xu Xiao.

03:39.160 --> 03:40.220
You even know this.

03:40.480 --> 03:42.360
Because when repairing the ancient kiln at the Imperial Kiln Factory,

03:42.360 --> 03:43.760
I actually moved bricks.

03:48.280 --> 03:48.880
Mr. Wei,

03:49.920 --> 03:51.380
can we discuss something?

03:52.040 --> 03:52.480
Go ahead.

03:52.480 --> 03:54.740
When you open the kiln in a couple of days,

03:55.079 --> 03:56.340
these students of mine

03:56.480 --> 03:58.880
will all come to observe and learn from you,

03:59.240 --> 04:00.300
and lend you a hand.

04:00.600 --> 04:01.680
So many people?

04:02.280 --> 04:03.410
I can't handle them.

04:04.440 --> 04:05.560
Pick two.

04:07.560 --> 04:08.160
Then,

04:08.920 --> 04:09.400
you

04:10.360 --> 04:10.880
and you.

04:11.080 --> 04:11.680
You two,

04:11.800 --> 04:13.460
have them come over on Sunday.

04:14.440 --> 04:16.160
Why us two?

04:16.360 --> 04:18.399
There's no why.

04:19.920 --> 04:21.850
Can't I just randomly pick you two?

04:21.880 --> 04:23.480
In a picturesque place like this,

04:23.480 --> 04:24.480
not falling in love

04:24.480 --> 04:26.320
would be a waste of the beautiful scenery.

04:26.320 --> 04:27.080
Yue.

04:27.360 --> 04:29.160
You have it easy leading a class.

04:29.400 --> 04:30.200
What's wrong?

04:30.400 --> 04:32.659
With so many students, you have choices.

04:33.320 --> 04:34.240
Unlike me,

04:35.280 --> 04:36.240
I only have one.

04:37.280 --> 04:37.880
Mr. Wei,

04:38.400 --> 04:39.000
you are

04:39.440 --> 04:40.770
more dedicated than me.

04:41.520 --> 04:42.600
We all know that.

04:43.280 --> 04:44.480
Come on. Let's start.

04:54.360 --> 04:54.960
Thank you.

04:56.760 --> 04:59.020
Your explanation today was really good.

04:59.360 --> 05:00.760
Next time you come to the imperial kiln,

05:00.760 --> 05:02.220
just contact me directly.

05:11.720 --> 05:13.050
Let's go sit over there.

05:13.480 --> 05:13.920
Okay.

05:42.440 --> 05:43.880
The weather is really nice today.

05:43.880 --> 05:44.200
Yes.

05:44.440 --> 05:46.680
Because Jingdezhen has a subtropical monsoon climate,

05:46.680 --> 05:47.400
and is surrounded by mountains,

05:47.400 --> 05:49.120
it has plenty of sunlight and distinct seasons.

05:49.120 --> 05:51.380
The temperature is mild and humid, so...

05:53.159 --> 05:55.620
Sorry, I seem to be explaining things again.

06:06.240 --> 06:08.080
Are you busy at school recently?

06:09.080 --> 06:09.960
It's okay.

06:10.320 --> 06:11.320
Recently, Mr. Liang

06:11.320 --> 06:13.000
taught us the craft of Tang Tri-colored Glazed Pottery.

06:13.000 --> 06:14.880
Mr. Yue taught us kintsugi.

06:14.880 --> 06:16.240
Mr. Lin also taught us about

06:16.240 --> 06:17.570
many types of ceramics.

06:17.720 --> 06:18.200
I

06:18.560 --> 06:19.960
have learned quite a lot.

06:22.640 --> 06:23.880
That is quite a lot.

06:36.680 --> 06:37.240
Yuexin.

06:39.920 --> 06:41.520
I have something to tell you.

06:44.040 --> 06:46.700
I've kept these words in my heart for a long time.

06:47.760 --> 06:49.490
I've always wanted to tell you.

06:52.640 --> 06:53.320
I like you.

06:58.560 --> 06:59.080
Yuexin,

07:00.480 --> 07:01.740
will you go out with me?

07:32.960 --> 07:34.600
Sorry, I have something to do.

07:34.600 --> 07:35.860
I have to go back first.

07:36.640 --> 07:37.760
I...

07:38.200 --> 07:39.000
I'll walk you.

07:39.320 --> 07:40.000
No, no need.

07:40.000 --> 07:41.120
I can go by myself.

08:05.040 --> 08:05.640
Xiaocen.

08:05.640 --> 08:06.240
Hello.

08:06.240 --> 08:06.840
Xiaocen.

08:06.840 --> 08:07.680
Xiaocen.

08:08.280 --> 08:09.610
What are you doing here?

08:09.760 --> 08:11.420
I... I'm just zoning out here.

08:11.840 --> 08:13.600
We found an interesting restaurant for tonight.

08:13.600 --> 08:14.760
Wang Lin went ahead to line up.

08:14.760 --> 08:16.120
Do you want to come with us?

08:16.120 --> 08:18.380
What if Xiaocen has other plans tonight?

08:18.560 --> 08:20.480
She's just standing here. What could she possibly have to do?

08:20.480 --> 08:20.840
Yeah.

08:20.840 --> 08:21.440
Didn't you say

08:21.440 --> 08:23.240
we should invite her to everything?

08:23.240 --> 08:23.970
Come with us.

08:24.360 --> 08:25.280
Let's go.

08:26.800 --> 08:27.660
So many people.

08:28.520 --> 08:28.980
Xu Xiao.

08:30.240 --> 08:31.200
We're grabbing dinner tonight.

08:31.200 --> 08:32.260
Wanna come with us?

08:33.679 --> 08:35.539
You guys are going out for dinner?

08:36.679 --> 08:37.120
Yeah.

08:39.960 --> 08:41.490
I have other plans tonight.

08:41.520 --> 08:42.039
I won't be joining you.

08:42.039 --> 08:42.760
What plans?

08:43.679 --> 08:44.159
I'm off.

08:46.920 --> 08:47.560
Xu Xiao.

08:53.200 --> 08:54.600
How about going tonight?

08:54.920 --> 08:56.580
You have nothing to do anyway.

08:57.240 --> 08:59.300
How do you know if he has nothing to do?

08:59.560 --> 09:00.820
Because we originally

09:01.200 --> 09:02.840
planned to eat together.

09:04.600 --> 09:05.730
What does that mean?

09:13.720 --> 09:14.240
Oh my god.

09:14.240 --> 09:15.880
I told you there was something going on between them.

09:15.880 --> 09:17.040
I told you so.

09:17.040 --> 09:17.760
Wait, since when?

09:17.760 --> 09:19.360
Xiaocen just made it public like that?

09:19.360 --> 09:20.960
Aren't these my lovely students?

09:20.960 --> 09:22.600
What are you doing?

09:29.640 --> 09:31.600
Alright, see you in class tomorrow.

09:31.600 --> 09:32.730
Goodbye, Mr. Liang.

09:33.360 --> 09:35.440
This is youth. Youth.

09:35.760 --> 09:36.480
Hurry up and tell us,

09:36.480 --> 09:37.120
you two.

09:37.120 --> 09:38.320
When did this happen?

09:38.800 --> 09:40.040
When did this happen? Tell us.

09:40.040 --> 09:41.520
Details, details, details!

09:41.520 --> 09:42.080
Tell us, tell us, tell us!

09:42.080 --> 09:43.340
I'll tell you tonight.

10:02.880 --> 10:04.340
Why is there no water here?

10:04.720 --> 10:05.200
Yuexin.

10:25.280 --> 10:26.400
You two chat first.

10:26.400 --> 10:28.040
I'll go buy some water.

10:45.480 --> 10:48.340
Why didn't you tell me you came to the Imperial Kiln?

10:48.880 --> 10:50.280
Yan Xue dragged me here.

10:51.080 --> 10:52.920
I was afraid of disturbing your work.

10:52.920 --> 10:53.800
So I...

10:54.120 --> 10:55.650
You weren't looking for me.

11:01.160 --> 11:02.090
About last time,

11:02.800 --> 11:03.400
I'm sorry.

11:03.960 --> 11:04.840
I scared you.

11:06.640 --> 11:06.960
No.

11:07.480 --> 11:08.000
I...

11:09.040 --> 11:09.640
If

11:10.200 --> 11:11.860
you haven't made up your mind,

11:12.720 --> 11:14.380
I can prove it with my actions.

11:18.960 --> 11:20.320
If you don't like me,

11:21.240 --> 11:22.500
just tell me directly.

11:22.920 --> 11:23.640
It's okay.

11:23.880 --> 11:24.280
I...

11:24.480 --> 11:26.360
I don't want you to feel too much pressure.

11:26.360 --> 11:26.720
I...

11:35.840 --> 11:37.800
It's actually not like that.

11:40.440 --> 11:41.920
Since we met,

11:42.320 --> 11:45.120
you've always been the one taking the initiative.

11:45.920 --> 11:47.560
I know you care about me a lot.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.800
When I was in a bad mood,

11:50.920 --> 11:52.780
you were the one who cheered me up.

11:52.840 --> 11:54.770
Whenever I ran into difficulties,

11:54.800 --> 11:57.130
you always actively helped me solve them.

11:59.040 --> 12:02.240
Actually, I know how you feel.

12:03.640 --> 12:04.900
Then what do you think?

12:07.040 --> 12:07.840
I'm scared.

12:08.200 --> 12:08.920
Scared?

12:12.560 --> 12:13.480
I think

12:13.680 --> 12:15.800
you seem very good at talking to girls

12:17.440 --> 12:19.440
and you're a few years older than me.

12:20.040 --> 12:21.240
So I thought

12:21.240 --> 12:23.440
you could easily fall for someone else.

12:23.960 --> 12:24.400
I...

12:25.160 --> 12:25.840
Actually,

12:26.000 --> 12:27.840
um, Yan Xue is still waiting for me.

12:27.840 --> 12:28.700
I'll get going.

12:44.920 --> 12:45.600
Cencen.

12:46.640 --> 12:48.000
Come out and have some steamed egg.

12:48.000 --> 12:49.080
I saw you didn't eat much for dinner.

12:49.080 --> 12:50.520
Is your stomach hurting again?

12:50.520 --> 12:52.080
No, I'm reviewing.

12:53.280 --> 12:53.880
It's fine.

13:00.640 --> 13:01.440
Cencen.

13:03.120 --> 13:05.250
I brought you a hot water bottle. Here.

13:05.600 --> 13:06.060
Hold it.

13:06.640 --> 13:08.480
Mom, I don't want it. It's too hot.

13:08.480 --> 13:09.360
What do you mean too hot?

13:09.360 --> 13:10.560
The heat will make you feel better.

13:10.560 --> 13:11.600
Don't I know you?

13:11.720 --> 13:12.560
Okay.

13:13.680 --> 13:15.140
Alright, I'm heading out.

13:17.520 --> 13:18.440
Cencen.

13:19.120 --> 13:20.600
Here, some tomatoes.

13:20.680 --> 13:21.880
Tomatoes.

13:21.920 --> 13:23.120
I'll leave them here.

13:23.320 --> 13:23.800
This way,

13:23.800 --> 13:24.860
it's easier to eat.

13:25.200 --> 13:25.920
Okay.

13:25.960 --> 13:28.200
Sister, just let Xiaocen be by herself.

13:28.200 --> 13:29.720
She is studying.

13:29.920 --> 13:31.320
I know.

13:31.960 --> 13:33.120
It's the weekend,

13:33.120 --> 13:35.160
why do they assign you so many things?

13:35.160 --> 13:36.320
Why do we even have weekends then?

13:36.320 --> 13:37.720
It means there is time to study,

13:37.720 --> 13:38.840
and time to rest.

13:38.840 --> 13:39.680
If you don't rest well,

13:39.680 --> 13:40.940
how can you study well?

13:41.880 --> 13:42.640
If it doesn't work out,

13:42.640 --> 13:44.760
I'll ask your class teacher for a leave.

13:44.760 --> 13:45.200
Mom,

13:45.360 --> 13:46.480
this is a rare opportunity.

13:46.480 --> 13:47.560
Just let me go.

13:47.840 --> 13:48.320
Come on, Mom.

13:48.320 --> 13:49.120
But aren't you feeling unwell?

13:49.120 --> 13:49.800
Mom, go out.

13:49.800 --> 13:51.280
I will definitely eat the tomatoes.

13:51.280 --> 13:52.320
Don't push me.

13:52.520 --> 13:53.200
You go out first.

13:53.200 --> 13:54.160
You sit.

13:54.640 --> 13:55.280
Okay.

13:55.560 --> 13:56.240
You sit.

13:59.000 --> 14:00.660
Put the hot water bottle back.

14:01.240 --> 14:02.240
Got it.

14:04.760 --> 14:05.760
Eat the tomatoes.

14:07.280 --> 14:08.320
Rest early.

14:22.200 --> 14:22.760
How is it?

14:23.160 --> 14:24.290
How are you feeling?

14:24.720 --> 14:25.680
What do you mean?

14:25.680 --> 14:26.960
Tell me. Don't dawdle.

14:27.720 --> 14:28.720
It's just that...

14:28.800 --> 14:29.330
Xiaocen,

14:29.600 --> 14:30.800
you've been spending so much time

14:30.800 --> 14:32.280
alone with Xu Xiao in Weijiayao lately.

14:32.280 --> 14:33.200
How far have you two progressed?

14:33.200 --> 14:34.480
Yeah, how far have you progressed?

14:34.480 --> 14:35.960
Not very far.

14:37.120 --> 14:38.120
And...

14:39.560 --> 14:40.890
What's wrong, Xiaocen?

14:41.600 --> 14:43.920
We even had a little argument.

14:44.720 --> 14:45.920
What's going on here?

14:48.120 --> 14:50.780
So what's the progress between you and Xiaocen?

14:52.200 --> 14:53.200
It's a long story.

14:56.880 --> 14:59.000
That day, right as we arrived at Master Wei's door,

14:59.000 --> 15:01.460
we heard the sound of porcelain shattering.

15:01.920 --> 15:02.450
Let's go.

15:05.040 --> 15:05.700
Master Wei.

15:07.640 --> 15:08.170
Guan Lin.

15:08.280 --> 15:08.810
Guan Lin.

15:10.440 --> 15:11.440
I'll go after him.

15:11.480 --> 15:13.140
Ask him what really happened.

15:25.880 --> 15:26.480
Guan Lin,

15:27.440 --> 15:28.300
what happened?

15:29.240 --> 15:30.120
Nothing.

15:30.880 --> 15:31.920
What could happen to me?

15:31.920 --> 15:33.200
So the Spring brings good fortune and harmony fat belly vase

15:33.200 --> 15:34.400
that Mr. Wei smashed just now,

15:34.400 --> 15:35.680
Yes, I made it.

15:38.440 --> 15:40.440
I don't know much about high-temperature color glaze,

15:40.440 --> 15:41.720
but I know that the Spring brings good fortune and harmony fat belly vase

15:41.720 --> 15:43.180
is extremely hard to make.

15:43.560 --> 15:45.120
And judging by the glaze color,

15:45.120 --> 15:46.250
it's a masterpiece.

15:46.800 --> 15:47.840
Why did Mr. Wei...

15:50.280 --> 15:52.410
He just doesn't want to acknowledge me

15:52.600 --> 15:54.860
or let me touch the Wei family's old kiln.

15:56.560 --> 15:57.360
Xu Xiao,

15:57.760 --> 15:59.220
I developed the technique

15:59.360 --> 16:01.440
and made that fat belly vase myself.

16:01.600 --> 16:02.680
Everyone in the village said it was good,

16:02.680 --> 16:03.640
but he said it wasn't

16:03.640 --> 16:05.160
and smashed it right away.

16:07.200 --> 16:08.530
What did the master say?

16:12.360 --> 16:12.880
Yes,

16:13.720 --> 16:14.800
I smashed it.

16:16.440 --> 16:16.960
Mr. Wei,

16:16.960 --> 16:19.160
why did you smash Guan Lin's porcelain?

16:19.640 --> 16:21.040
It turned out like that.

16:21.800 --> 16:23.240
Shouldn't I smash it?

16:25.440 --> 16:26.160
Mr. Wei,

16:27.360 --> 16:29.600
no matter how Guan Lin did,

16:31.200 --> 16:33.240
aren't you being too harsh on him?

16:34.240 --> 16:35.160
Xiaocen,

16:35.840 --> 16:36.960
do you know

16:37.080 --> 16:40.080
how many people don't value the art of kiln firing?

16:40.280 --> 16:42.120
It's too dirty and tiring.

16:42.640 --> 16:45.440
Plus, modern kilns have their own firing methods.

16:45.440 --> 16:46.520
What they value

16:46.800 --> 16:47.960
is heat utilization

16:48.560 --> 16:50.480
and temperature measurement equipment.

16:50.480 --> 16:52.400
No one values kiln firing.

16:52.920 --> 16:54.680
They say it's only a matter of time

16:54.680 --> 16:56.160
before this job is eliminated.

16:56.160 --> 16:57.480
I don't think so.

16:59.200 --> 17:00.440
On the contrary,

17:01.040 --> 17:01.960
kiln firing

17:02.240 --> 17:03.640
is the most important part

17:03.640 --> 17:07.720
of the traditional Chai Kiln firing process.

17:08.560 --> 17:10.599
I can't let such a heavy responsibility

17:10.599 --> 17:12.400
end with my apprentice.

17:14.520 --> 17:15.980
So if he makes it like that,

17:16.160 --> 17:17.319
it must be smashed.

17:21.160 --> 17:21.800
Xu Xiao,

17:22.560 --> 17:23.280
do you know?

17:23.720 --> 17:24.599
From the first day

17:24.599 --> 17:26.000
I became his apprentice,

17:26.599 --> 17:28.400
he showed me his medical report.

17:29.560 --> 17:30.490
Stomach cancer.

17:31.480 --> 17:32.160
What?

17:33.000 --> 17:34.400
The master has cancer,

17:34.720 --> 17:37.250
why is the apprentice still arguing with him?

17:37.320 --> 17:38.780
Actually, I think Guan Lin

17:39.120 --> 17:40.250
has his own reasons.

17:42.840 --> 17:44.560
But Mr. Wei looks so healthy.

17:45.080 --> 17:46.520
I thought he was perfectly fine.

17:46.520 --> 17:47.480
You're right.

17:47.720 --> 17:48.720
He is fine.

17:49.880 --> 17:51.040
The doctor said at the time

17:51.040 --> 17:52.440
he only had three months left.

17:52.440 --> 17:53.320
I pitied him,

17:53.480 --> 17:54.840
so I stayed to take care of him.

17:54.840 --> 17:56.680
I really don't want anything in return.

17:56.680 --> 17:57.200
I just

17:57.480 --> 17:59.200
respect a senior like him from the bottom of my heart.

17:59.200 --> 17:59.840
Yes.

17:59.840 --> 18:02.160
There aren't many master kiln operators like Mr. Wei in Jingdezhen.

18:02.160 --> 18:03.020
I can count them

18:03.400 --> 18:04.560
on one hand.

18:04.880 --> 18:05.280
Right.

18:06.120 --> 18:07.000
But Xu Xiao,

18:08.000 --> 18:08.920
Three months.

18:10.040 --> 18:11.800
That was five years ago.

18:12.640 --> 18:13.520
In these five years,

18:13.520 --> 18:16.000
I fed him, made his bed, and cleaned up after him.

18:16.000 --> 18:16.930
For three years,

18:17.080 --> 18:18.480
I barely even went home.

18:18.960 --> 18:21.560
Now he eats well and sleeps soundly.

18:21.880 --> 18:23.840
He's getting stronger every day.

18:24.080 --> 18:25.810
I feel like he might outlive me.

18:26.240 --> 18:26.600
Yes.

18:27.080 --> 18:28.800
Guan Lin, it's been hard on you.

18:28.800 --> 18:29.680
You can all see

18:30.480 --> 18:31.360
how hard he is to please.

18:31.360 --> 18:32.420
He has a huge temper

18:32.480 --> 18:33.680
and is picky about his food.

18:33.680 --> 18:34.320
As for vegetables,

18:34.320 --> 18:35.480
he insists on growing them himself.

18:35.480 --> 18:37.610
Why doesn't he raise pigs himself too?

18:38.320 --> 18:39.520
He refuses to go to the hospital,

18:39.520 --> 18:40.480
refuses to get injections,

18:40.480 --> 18:41.520
and refuses to take medicine.

18:41.520 --> 18:42.680
Every time we go to the hospital,

18:42.680 --> 18:44.360
it's like coaxing a child.

18:44.480 --> 18:46.160
If I'm not paying attention, he's off smoking

18:46.160 --> 18:46.960
or drinking.

18:47.640 --> 18:49.300
Do you know what he's taught me

18:49.720 --> 18:50.920
in these three years?

18:51.320 --> 18:52.200
Look at me.

18:54.840 --> 18:55.440
Spitting.

18:55.680 --> 18:56.320
Just this.

18:57.160 --> 18:59.280
He says that at the critical moment,

18:59.280 --> 19:00.800
you can estimate the temperature

19:00.800 --> 19:01.960
based on how the spit burns

19:01.960 --> 19:03.040
when you spit into the kiln.

19:03.040 --> 19:03.900
I believed him.

19:04.200 --> 19:05.200
But just for this,

19:06.120 --> 19:07.120
it shouldn't take three years, right?

19:07.120 --> 19:07.640
Yes.

19:09.240 --> 19:11.720
Speaking of spitting,

19:12.880 --> 19:15.240
it's about observing how the spit burns

19:15.560 --> 19:17.320
to help judge the temperature.

19:18.480 --> 19:20.200
It sounds simple,

19:20.480 --> 19:22.080
but there are very few people

19:22.080 --> 19:23.610
who can actually master it.

19:24.920 --> 19:26.360
Besides, nowadays,

19:26.880 --> 19:28.480
there's temperature-measuring equipment.

19:28.480 --> 19:30.800
Electric kilns make firing even easier.

19:31.840 --> 19:32.320
Then,

19:32.720 --> 19:36.360
why is it that the things fired in kilns

19:36.360 --> 19:38.240
from any other country in the world

19:38.240 --> 19:40.120
cannot be compared with the things

19:40.120 --> 19:41.520
fired in our traditional

19:41.520 --> 19:43.440
Chinese kilns?

19:44.480 --> 19:45.400
That is because

19:45.920 --> 19:47.050
the art of porcelain

19:47.440 --> 19:49.520
is the art of fire.

19:52.240 --> 19:54.120
In all my years as an apprentice,

19:54.440 --> 19:57.400
I've seen so many firing failures.

19:58.880 --> 20:00.200
That brat Guan Lin,

20:00.520 --> 20:02.320
he's seen too few.

20:05.240 --> 20:06.000
Mr. Wei.

20:06.680 --> 20:08.740
Experience isn't gained overnight.

20:09.400 --> 20:11.930
You have to let Guan Lin experience it slowly.

20:13.920 --> 20:15.920
I'm afraid there's no time.

20:19.840 --> 20:22.440
So the master and apprentice just fell out like that.

20:22.440 --> 20:24.440
Then what did you and Xu Xiao do next?

20:39.560 --> 20:40.160
Mr. Wei,

20:41.600 --> 20:42.520
these sherds,

20:43.360 --> 20:44.490
can I take them back?

20:47.160 --> 20:48.360
Do whatever you want.

21:02.120 --> 21:02.800
Xu Xiao,

21:03.360 --> 21:05.690
how did you persuade Guan Lin to come back?

21:07.480 --> 21:09.540
Guan Lin didn't really want to leave.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.600
He just felt too wronged.

21:13.120 --> 21:14.720
He did so much for his master,

21:14.880 --> 21:16.480
but still couldn't get recognized.

21:16.480 --> 21:18.240
Actually, I don't understand either.

21:18.240 --> 21:19.570
Mr. Wei is in poor health

21:19.840 --> 21:21.920
and has only Guan Lin as his apprentice.

21:21.920 --> 21:23.520
Why can't he let him take over as soon as possible?

21:23.520 --> 21:24.760
What Mr. Wei wants to pass on

21:24.760 --> 21:26.090
is his lifelong skills,

21:26.680 --> 21:28.640
so he has to be stricter with his evaluation.

21:28.640 --> 21:30.560
But he shouldn't dismiss Guan Lin.

21:30.560 --> 21:32.960
Everyone has their own independent thoughts.

21:32.960 --> 21:35.360
A master shouldn't impart knowledge on the one hand,

21:35.360 --> 21:36.290
and on the other,

21:36.520 --> 21:38.280
tightly control his apprentice.

21:38.280 --> 21:40.410
I think Mr. Wei means well for Guan Lin.

21:41.200 --> 21:43.440
Look, he only has Guan Lin as his apprentice.

21:43.440 --> 21:44.370
Just like my mom.

21:45.560 --> 21:47.420
I know she sacrificed a lot for me.

21:47.840 --> 21:50.920
Even though there are some things I just can't understand.

21:50.920 --> 21:52.650
But you are different from her.

21:52.720 --> 21:53.640
Maybe you are just forcing yourself

21:53.640 --> 21:54.920
to accept it.

22:05.800 --> 22:07.060
No, I didn't mean that.

22:22.320 --> 22:24.450
So did you and Xu Xiao make up in the end?

22:25.400 --> 22:26.520
Actually, I

22:27.040 --> 22:29.300
don't even know if it counts as making up.

22:30.440 --> 22:33.040
And I don't even know if that counted as a fight.

22:33.760 --> 22:34.760
Then go coax her.

22:37.320 --> 22:38.980
I don't know how to coax girls.

22:39.720 --> 22:40.720
Coaxing girls,

22:40.840 --> 22:41.880
I'm very good at it.

22:41.880 --> 22:43.000
Why didn't you ask me?

22:43.000 --> 22:43.960
I can teach you.

22:45.000 --> 22:45.600
Thank you.

22:46.000 --> 22:47.160
You're welcome.

22:49.960 --> 22:51.020
Where is Zhuoting?

22:52.000 --> 22:52.880
Zhuoting?

22:54.400 --> 22:56.000
He went on a date with Xiaoyi.

22:57.400 --> 22:58.040
Sorry.

22:58.880 --> 22:59.480
It's fine.

22:59.920 --> 23:00.760
I've moved on.

24:23.240 --> 24:23.720
Hello.

24:24.040 --> 24:24.480
Sir.

24:25.760 --> 24:27.160
I want to look at the cups.

24:27.440 --> 24:28.960
Which surname are you looking for?

24:28.960 --> 24:29.960
Do you have Zhang?

24:30.400 --> 24:31.000
Yes, we do.

25:36.640 --> 25:37.360
I'm sorry.

25:38.560 --> 25:39.960
Earlier on the mountain,

25:40.880 --> 25:42.140
I said the wrong thing.

25:45.800 --> 25:47.720
You were the one who wouldn't talk to me.

25:47.720 --> 25:48.980
I thought you were mad,

25:49.840 --> 25:50.900
so I didn't dare to.

25:52.560 --> 25:54.280
Actually, I wasn't mad.

25:57.040 --> 25:58.840
You just hit the nail on the head,

25:58.840 --> 25:59.770
so I got anxious.

26:00.760 --> 26:02.690
I really do always listen to my mom.

26:03.840 --> 26:05.240
I didn't mean it that way.

26:06.640 --> 26:08.900
Actually, just like Mr. Wei and Guan Lin,

26:09.400 --> 26:10.920
they don't have any fundamental conflicts.

26:10.920 --> 26:12.280
They just didn't put themselves

26:12.280 --> 26:13.480
in the other's shoes.

26:14.800 --> 26:16.660
I didn't consider your feelings.

26:21.280 --> 26:22.540
I accept your apology.

26:24.200 --> 26:24.800
I'm sorry.

26:26.600 --> 26:27.320
Can you forgive me?
